00:56:33.430 --> 00:56:34.730
&gt;&gt; John Haskell: Tough question.

00:56:34.730 --> 00:56:36.890
Either of you guys
want to say something.

00:56:36.890 --> 00:56:38.710
&gt;&gt; Yuval Levin: Sure,
